{
  "stem": "19982.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- and, you know, Chamberlain gave away part of Czechoslovakia to Germany, and the part of Czechoslovakia Poland took.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1939, this was-- the-- I remember 1939, end of 1939, the beginning-- end of '38, the beginning of '39, I went with my mother to Zakopane.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was-- at this time, there was-- the Olympics was in Zakopane-- the Winter Olympics.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember when we were going and how beautiful it was there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, I mean, this was my best memory, which I really could remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A wonderful time we had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father came, like, once or twice for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Zakopane was far away from us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was quite a few hours by train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember even which hotel we stayed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were staying in [NON-ENGLISH], and the street was called Droga Do Bialego.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I had such a wonderful time there that it's remained in my memory, even the address of the hotel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we saw the Winter Olympics, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came from all there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, yes-- there we did experience anti-Semitism, because I remember we took a tour to the-- to a place there in the-- in the high mountains.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were-- it was a tour.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were a lot of Pollacks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were making fun of Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were saying what to do with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, like we don't need them, we-- and I also heard-- you know, there is anti-Semitism-- that they say, you know, you're-- shouldn't buy by Jews.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You should-- there was one senator which said, we shouldn't-- we are civilized people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We shouldn't kill Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we should make a boycott for-- so they will leave.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
